transition on ID to state [230]

-------------------
lalr_state [230]: {
  [expression ::= ID (*) , {LPAREN RPAREN MAS MENOS DIVISION DOSPUNTOS PCOMA }]
  [expression ::= ID (*) NUMERO , {LPAREN RPAREN MAS MENOS DIVISION DOSPUNTOS PCOMA }]
}

}

lalr_state [252]: {
  [parentesis ::= LPAREN (*) expression operamesta expression extraperamesta RPAREN , {LPAREN RPAREN MAS MENOS DIVISION PCOMA }]
  [parentesis ::= (*) LPAREN expression operamesta expression extraperamesta RPAREN , {MAS MENOS DIVISION }]
  [parentesis ::= LPAREN (*) parentesis operamesta parentesis extraparentesis RPAREN , {LPAREN RPAREN MAS MENOS DIVISION PCOMA }]
  [parentesis ::= (*) LPAREN parentesis operamesta parentesis extraparentesis RPAREN , {MAS MENOS DIVISION }]
  [parentesis ::= LPAREN (*) expression RPAREN , {LPAREN RPAREN MAS MENOS DIVISION PCOMA }]
  [parentesis ::= LPAREN (*) parentesis operamesta expression RPAREN , {LPAREN RPAREN MAS MENOS DIVISION PCOMA }]

  [expression ::= (*) ID NUMERO , {DOSPUNTOS }]
  [expression ::= (*) NUMERO , {DOSPUNTOS }]
}

  [instruccion ::= SI LPAREN condicion RPAREN THEN instrucciones FIN (*) , {CHALE DELAY TMR0 PA PB PC PD PE TA TB TC TD TE ANSEL ANSELH TA0 TA1 TA2 TA3 TA4 TA5 TA6 TA7 TB0 TB1 TB2 TB3 TB4 TB5 TB6 TB7 TC0 TC1 TC2 TC3 TC4 TC5 TC6 TC7 TD0 TD1 TD2 TD3 TD4 TD5 TD6 TD7 TE0 TE1 TE2 TE3 PA0 PA1 PA2 PA3 PA4 PA5 PA6 PA7 PB0 PB1 PB2 PB3 PB4 PB5 PB6 PB7 PC0 PC1 PC2 PC3 PC4 PC5 PC6 PC7 PD0 PD1 PD2 PD3 PD4 PD5 PD6 PD7 PE0 PE1 PE2 PE3 ANSEL0 ANSEL1 ANSEL2 ANSEL3 ANSEL4 ANSEL5 ANSEL6 ANSEL7 ANSELH0 ANSELH1 ANSELH2 ANSELH3 ANSELH4 ANSELH5 OPTIONREG_INTEDG OPTIONREG_PS OPTIONREG_T0CS OPTIONREG_T0SE OPTIONREG_PSA OPTIONREG_PS2 OPTIONREG_PS1 OPTIONREG_PS0 OPTIONREG_RBPU INTCON INTCONGIE INTCONPEIE INTCONT0IE INTCONINTE INTCONRBIE INTCONT0IF INTCONINTF INTCONRBIF ADCON0_ADCS1 ADCON0_ADCS0 ADCON0_CHS3 ADCON0_CHS2 ADCON0_CHS1 ADCON0_CHS0 ADCON0_GO ADCON0_ADON ADCON1_ADFM ADCON1_VCFG1 ADCON1_VCFG0 NO FIN SWITCH OTHERWISE RLLAVE TIPOVC RETURN ID SI CASO WHILE }]
}
